doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    title Digitalising SRM IST
    link(href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet', integrity='sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi', crossorigin='anonymous')
  body(style='background-color: #e3f2fd;')
    nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg(style='background-color: #e3f2fd;')
      .container-fluid
        img.attachment-full.size-full.lazy.loaded(width='200', height='103', src='https://d23qowwaqkh3fj.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/srm-logo-white.svg.gzip', data-src='https://d23qowwaqkh3fj.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/srm-logo-white.svg.gzip', alt='', data-was-processed='true')
        a.navbar-brand(href='#')
        button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
          span.navbar-toggler-icon
        #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
          ul.navbar-nav.me-auto.mb-2.mb-lg-0
            li.nav-item.active
              a.nav-link.mx-4(aria-current='page', href='/') Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.mx-4(href='./about') About
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.mx-4(href='./contact') Contact-us
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.mx-4(href='./campuslife') Campus Life
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.mx-4(href='./placement') Placements
          form.d-flex(role='search')
            input.form-control.me-2(type='search', placeholder='Search', aria-label='Search')
            button.btn.btn-outline-success(type='submit') Search
    #carouselExampleCaptions.carousel.slide.carousel-fade(data-bs-ride='false')
      .carousel-indicators
        button.active(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselExampleCaptions', data-bs-slide-to='0', aria-current='true', aria-label='Slide 1')
        button(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselExampleCaptions', data-bs-slide-to='1', aria-label='Slide 2')
        button(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselExampleCaptions', data-bs-slide-to='2', aria-label='Slide 3')
      .carousel-inner
        .carousel-item.active
          img.d-block.w-100(src='/images/22.png', alt='...')
          .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
            h2 Welcome to SRM
            p SRM Institute of Science and Technology
        .carousel-item
          img.d-block.w-100(src='/images/11.jpg', alt='...')
          .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
            h2 Best place to grow and learn
            p SRM Institute of Science and Technology
        .carousel-item
          img.d-block.w-100(src='/images/33.jpg', alt='...')
          .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
            h2 Award Winnnig Research Programms
            p SRM Institute of Science and Technology
      button.carousel-control-prev(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselExampleCaptions', data-bs-slide='prev')
        span.carousel-control-prev-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        span.visually-hidden Previous
      button.carousel-control-next(type='button', data-bs-target='#carouselExampleCaptions', data-bs-slide='next')
        span.carousel-control-next-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        span.visually-hidden Next
    .container.my-4
      .row.featurette.d-flex.justify-content-center.align-items-center
        .col-md-7
          h2.featurette-heading.fw-normal.lh-1
            | Fantastic Placement records.
            span.text-muted Get your dream job.
          p.lead
            | A total of 1,050 companies visited the campus and more than 10,000 students were placed during SRM Institute of Science and Technology placements 2022. Further, the SRM University highest package offered in 2022 stood at INR 100 LPA..
        .col-md-5
          img.bd-placeholder-img.bd-placeholder-img-lg.featurette-image.img-fluid.mx-auto(src='./images/pl-1.jpeg', width='400', height='300', alt='')
    .container.my-4
      .row.featurette.d-flex.justify-content-center.align-items-center
        .col-md-7.order-md-2
          h2.featurette-heading.fw-normal.lh-1
            | SRM Institute of Science and Technology.
            span.text-muted Average Package 2022.
          p.lead
            | The average package offered to the students of CS and IT Department during SRM University Chennai placements 2022 stood at INR 9.5 LPA. An improving trend was witnessed in the average salary offered over the last three years during SRM Institute of Science and Technology placements. The average salary trends witnessed during SRM University placements over the past three years are presented below:.
        .col-md-5.order-md-1
          img.bd-placeholder-img.bd-placeholder-img-lg.featurette-image.img-fluid.mx-auto(src='./images/pl-2.jpeg', width='400', height='900', alt='')
    .container.my-4
      .row.featurette.d-flex.justify-content-center.align-items-center
        .col-md-7
          h2.featurette-heading.fw-normal.lh-1
            | SRM Institute of Science and Technology.
            span.text-muted Batch Placed Trends: 2019 vs 2020 vs 2021
          p.lead
            | An improving trend was witnessed in the no. of high paying recruiters over the last three years during SRM IST placements. The trends witnessed during SRM University placements over the last three years with respect to the high paying recruiters, high paying offers and day sharing offers are presented.
        .col-md-5
          img.bd-placeholder-img.bd-placeholder-img-lg.featurette-image.img-fluid.mx-auto(src='./images/pl-3.jpeg', width='400', height='400', alt='')
    .container.my-4
      .row.featurette.d-flex.justify-content-center.align-items-center
        .col-md-7.order-md-2
          h2.featurette-heading.fw-normal.lh-1
            | SRM Institute of Science and Technology.
            span.text-muted Highest Package 2022
          p.lead
            | The highest package offered during SRM Institute of Science and Technology placements 2022 stood at INR 100 LPA (INR 1 crore per annum). An improving trend was witnessed in the highest salary offered over the last two years during SRM IST placements. The highest salary trends witnessed during SRM University placements over the past two years are presented.
          p
        .col-md-5.order-md-1
          img.bd-placeholder-img.bd-placeholder-img-lg.featurette-image.img-fluid.mx-auto(src='./images/pl-4.jpeg', width='400', height='400', alt='')
    .container
      .container
        footer.py-3.my-4
          ul.nav.justify-content-center.border-bottom.pb-3.mb-3
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href='#') Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href='#') Campus Life
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href='#') Placements
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href='#') About
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link.px-2.text-muted(href='#') Contact-us
          p.text-center.text-muted SRM Institute of Science
